song.info: #feekzoid 12/10/95 #wooow... i like this #mod... (ego!) #its kind of a mix of #styles, from sort of #twinpeaksesque, to #trippy, mellow bits, #and a bit of homage #martin galway.. :) #this mod was a real #pain to do, bcoz #one sample - flutey #thing had a shitty #amount of 8-bit ring #in it, and i could #not get anyother sam #to suit the piece... #putting the filter #on doesnt wreck the# #mod, y'know... :( #turn it off if ya #like.... :p #anywayz, greets to #kenz,mat,bobo,fiend, #bod,jon,shamus, #and you... :d #i write this text on #the day that i becom #an uncle......... # bleurghh! ;) #just kidding, spoon!
